titleStmt.title: The Prince of Orange his third declaration
titleStmt.author: Speke, Hugh, 1656-1724?
William III, King of England, 1650-1702, attributed name.

notesStmt.note: A spurious declaration. In fact by Hugh Speke--Wing (CD-ROM edition).
At end of text: Given under our hand and seal at our Head-quarters at Sherburn-Castle, the 28th. day of November, 1688.
Reproduction of original in the Folger Shakespeare Library.
